{"tid":1583550,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"手足們 麻煩叫人唔好影相要禮貌啲","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T16:24:28.000Z","uid":154257,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82df1bd0d4228f78da4b09398c8dfd615e455d2d","tid":1583550,"uid":154257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"今日出咗荃灣人鏈，大概5點半左右愈黎愈多人喺綠楊坊物資站聚集。<br />\n<br />\n手足們見到2樓有人喺欄杆邊拎住電話都唔知係咪真係影緊相就開咪大屌，叫人落黎，咪撚影屌你老母等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白大家好緊張，但今日係中學生主場，大部分人都著緊校服，咁樣著校服嘅手足唔係咁好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家下次看到有人可能係影相嘅時候，心平氣和咁叫對方唔好影， <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以免傷及同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLast but not least <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d7f64884139c4c6fb95699bd20d94da302d1c77","tid":1583550,"uid":157891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"呢件事講咗三個月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該俾啲自制啦"},{"pid":"a87b330c1fdeb94d91cf93c2920f4d1c4f08231f","tid":1583550,"uid":154257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"禮貌十連推<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"effc4a9123552400ae1dd316d11b29269d8fbef1","tid":1583550,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"講咗100日"},{"pid":"f0e1452d02cd280c20fc9219705d1c1a198b0072","tid":1583550,"uid":15